mk.tmdb.core
Class URLCreator

java.lang.Object
  mk.tmdb.core.URLCreator

public class URLCreator
extends java.lang.Object

This class provides methods for creating well formed query URL. Before start to use this methods is needed setting the API Key otherwise the URL will be wrong.
